HEADWORD: Detrition
<hw>De*tri"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>detritio</ets>. See <er>Detriment</er>.]</ety> <def>A wearing off
or away.</def>⟦br⟧
